Source: hw-management
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Yehuda Yehudai <yyehudai@nvidia.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10.0.0)
Standards-Version: 3.9.8
Homepage: http://www.nvidia.com

Package: hw-management
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${dist:Depends}, lsb-base (>= 3.0-6), python2.7 | python3, python3-psutil, xxd, libiio-utils, dmidecode, i2c-tools
Description: Thermal control and chassis management for Nvidia systems (host)
 This package supports Nvidia switches family for chassis
 management and thermal control on the host CPU.

Package: hw-management-bmc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, systemd, udev
Description: Hardware management and chassis services for Nvidia BMC (SONiC BMC)
 This package provides BMC-side scripts, systemd units, udev rules,
 and platform-specific config (e.g. HI193 / SPC6 AST2700) for use
 with Microsoft Sonic BMC OS or other Debian-based BMC images.
